<article id="post-824" class="post-824 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-in-the-news tag-mmve tag-opensim">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/cgvw-to-host-mmve-2012/" rel="bookmark">CGVW to Host MMVE 2012</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><a title="MMVE Inworld by Diva Canto, on Flickr" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/20665379@N03/8033115902/"><img src="http://farm9.staticflickr.com/8456/8033115902_d2b058252e.jpg" alt="MMVE Inworld" width="400" height="218" /></a><br />
The Center is proud to be hosting the virtual conference for the <a href="http://www.pap.vs.uni-due.de/MMVE12/">5th International Workshop on Massively Multiuser Virtual Environments</a> (MMVE 2012), which will take place in real life in Munich, October 9. The virtual conference center, based on the <a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/?p=786">Universal Campus</a>, will host the Poster session, as well as the Town Hall meeting that will include  members of the community who are unable to attend the workshop in Munich.</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/b47940d743ed969c5df06ec0b2f66bbd?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/b47940d743ed969c5df06ec0b2f66bbd?s=98&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' /><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/author/lopes/">staff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/cgvw-to-host-mmve-2012/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2012-09-28T16:31:04+00:00">September 28, 2012</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/category/in-the-news/" rel="category tag">In the News</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/tag/mmve/" rel="tag">MMVE</a>, <a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/tag/opensim/" rel="tag">OpenSim</a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
