<article id="post-786" class="post-786 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-in-the-news tag-3d-collaboration-environments tag-opensim">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/the-universal-campus/" rel="bookmark">The Universal Campus</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><iframe src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/TkNA69AiL4A" frameborder="0" width="560" height="315"></iframe></p>
<p><a href="http://www.igb.uci.edu/~pfbaldi/">Pierre Baldi</a> and <a href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~lopes/">Cristina Videira Lopes</a> have developed an infrastructure called the <a href="http://universalcampus.igb.uci.edu/">Universal Campus</a>which allows, among other things, the organization and deployment of scientific meeting, conferences, classes, etc in a 3D virtual world. 2011. The work has been published in the <a href="http://elearnmag.acm.org/archive.cfm?aid=2206888" target="_blank">ACM ELearn magazine</a>.</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/b47940d743ed969c5df06ec0b2f66bbd?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/b47940d743ed969c5df06ec0b2f66bbd?s=98&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' /><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/author/lopes/">staff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/the-universal-campus/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2012-05-27T20:55:47+00:00">May 27, 2012</time><time class="updated" datetime="2012-09-28T15:48:57+00:00">September 28, 2012</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/category/in-the-news/" rel="category tag">In the News</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/tag/3d-collaboration-environments/" rel="tag">3D collaboration environments</a>, <a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/tag/opensim/" rel="tag">OpenSim</a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
